name.ja: <ruby>焔<rt>えん</rt></ruby><ruby>魔<rt>ま</rt></ruby><ruby>神<rt>じん</rt></ruby>ゼブルス

summoning_condition.en: You can Special Summon this card from your hand face-up to your field by sending 2 other cards from your hand to the Graveyard.

requirement.en: During your Main Phase that you Normal or Special Summoned this card.

effect.en: Special Summon 1 Level 10 FIRE Attribute Fiend Type monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position, except a monster with 2400 ATK. Then, you can change the battle position of 1 face-up Ritual Monster on your field.
